our research are summarized as follows: Port2vec can identify relevant similarities between container ship ports; and geographical analysis supports the effectiveness of the methodology.
This recommendation technology can be used only for container ports because it leverages sequences of berth records by treating them as textual sentences. In subsequent research, we intend to improve the approach to provide recommendations for other types of shipping.

