The results presented in Table 2 show that the ports with a high recommendation value have similar connections to internal transportation networks and are export-focused. The computational framework we developed will help shipping managers to choose alternative destination ports effectively, especially in a period of epidemic. This work can also help us to detect communities of port clusters in the future. V. CONCLUSION We used a novel approach to calculate the similarity using word embedding. This study demonstrates for the ﬁrst time that Port2vec technology, derived from word2vec, can be used effectively to provide port recommendations in shipping and maritime applications. The key points in

